	  <h3>1.Signing up</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>There are two ways to sign up. You can sign up through Facebook.Alternatively, you can sign up through email registration. When you sign up for an email, please fill email address, password, your name and date of birth.After signing up for membership, you must confirm the confirmation email to complete it. If you have not received the verification e-mail, please check the spam folder. If you have not received it yet, please contact us at info@rollerslab.com. We'll help you!</p>
	  </div>
	  <h3>2. Becoming a Roller</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>How to become a Roller is very simple. Please only authenticate your mobile phone. After you have confirmed your mobile phone number, you can register your travel items. Become a Roller to represent my city now. If you do not receive verification message, please contact info@rollerslab.com. We'll help you!</p>
	  </div>
	  <h3>3. Registering as a Guide</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>In order to be a guide in Rolling Potato, you need to present your Qualified Guide qualification. After registering your mobile phone number on the Guide Registration page, please attach your ID card and Tourism related certificate's photograph or a scanned image. We'll let you know within 3 business days!</p>
